Sounds to me like a software (read: 65816 code in the ROM/game itself) checksum problem of some sort -- lots of games can suffer from this issue.<br /><br />There is no evidence to suggest it's an anti-piracy effort, so that should be considered complete FUD at this point in time.  Please don't go that route.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3">koitsu</a> — Sun Jul 03, 2011 4:53 am</p><hr />
